# Ignore all Tesseract portable binaries and language data files.
# These are large binary files that should NOT be committed to the repository.
#
# Run  scripts/fetch_tesseract.py  to populate this directory automatically,
# or follow the manual instructions in  docs/ocr.md .
*
!.gitignore
!.gitkeep
# Allow the tessdata sub-directory itself (but not its contents)
!tessdata/
tessdata/*
!tessdata/.gitkeep
